name: Dr. Larry Leemis
title: Professor of Mathematics
quote: Jack's presentation [won] the people's choice. Perhaps not a coincidence that you were the strongest at creating your own data sets as opposed to using external data sets. Very strong start with the early jump from everyone to generate interest.

name: Dr. Qun Li
title: Professor of Computer Science
quote: Jack, you performed exceptionally well on the [Quantum Computing] final exam, earning the highest score (70/75). I believe you, among all students, have demonstrated the deepest understanding of the material we covered in class, and I commend you for that.
